snippet.title: Heartland 1.0 Trailer
snippet.description:
Now available - Heartland, a fantastic levelset by Skillsaw for Eternity. Links below.

I really enjoyed my time with the mod when I played it, so when the discussion of a possible trailer came up, I volunteered. Eternity needs more good mods, and this one needs all the attention it can get!

More information and Download link available here:
https://www.doomworld.com/forum/topic/120175/

Additionally, Heartland's OST by Stewboy is available here:
https://stuartrynn.bandcamp.com/album/doom-heartland-ost
